{"tid":1507550,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"配合神秘公眾活動 西環多條道路明早9時半間封","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T08:38:41.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"feefc32a10e41351c45177dd66ecbfed67ed8816","tid":1507550,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】警方將於明日實施特別交通安排，配合於港島舉行的一項公眾活動。<br />\n<br />\n下列道路將於上午9時30分起實施間歇性封閉，直至人群散去及交通回復正常為止：<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 皇后大道西；<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 屈地街；<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 朝光街；<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 德輔道西；<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 堅彌地城海旁；<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 山道；及<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 保德街。<br />\n<br />\n道路封閉期間，車輛將可能被禁止進出沿途的停車場。警方會視乎該區當時的交通及人潮情況實施交通安排。駕車人士應保持忍讓，並遵從現場警務人員的指示"},{"pid":"1a1d1500aa6fb9a089754723b152438318419bf5","tid":1507550,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:57:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=0cf25ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"8bdcea0ddf2b0860c8c1b619e958b165c520d457","tid":1507550,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"有冇link?"},{"pid":"47fdb4e7357d01b3fde536debd3ff3912563452f","tid":1507550,"uid":141157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"究竟係乜嘢活動，完全搵唔到相關資料"},{"pid":"50c69ef17807b4876fe73591c878e5583d633338","tid":1507550,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"&mdash; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">堅彌地城</span>海旁；"},{"pid":"e4b54012a827f2ae00b546e3aa3a8b325c