vY%3D&h=c2a40895\" target=\"_blank\">http://timable.com/en/event/1843017</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QNLbC63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNLbC63.jpg&h=12f02c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWinter on fire《凜冬烈火：烏克蘭自由之戰》<br />\n是一部2015年的紀錄片，由葉夫根尼&middot;艾菲尼夫斯基執導，紀錄了烏克蘭在2013年至2014年冬季爆發的親歐盟示威運動，這部紀錄片由烏克蘭、美國和英國聯合製作。本片於2015年10月9日在Netflix上釋出，在此之前曾數次參加電影節的展映。<br />\n<br />\nWinter on fire Trailer :<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RibAQHeDia8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRibAQHeDia8&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=e06fa49a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RibAQHeDia8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">31/8 (六) 下午三點 民陣「人大831落閘五周年」遊行  </span></span><br />\n留意活動詳情請去 主辦單位 - 民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front Facebook  : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=bd8e8569\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68885329_2426160977431279_3676885415790379008_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQkG9kPSM8fx54Bryd0nJu7rQtrRmaN-9gqpvISDgvWLXWBCHx51ze5VK9C7aGIpfRM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=6bbe560f355ad8edeba434eefd6aeccf&amp;oe=5DD25A85\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68885329_2426160977431279_3676885415790379008_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQkG9kPSM8fx54Bryd0nJu7rQtrRmaN-9gqpvISDgvWLXWBCHx51ze5VK9C7aGIpfRM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D6bbe560f355ad8edeba434eefd6aeccf%26oe%3D5DD25A85&h=ccadb53f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nearsnake.com/wp-content/uploads/cache